id":2303091,"uid":329350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5da8e349cd1c2985ae0f3a3a4b4288c82b3f83f","tid":2303091,"uid":150293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"唔好咁衝動<br />\n佢哋幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openup.hk/index.htm?lang=zh-Hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk%2Findex.htm%3Flang%3Dzh-Hant&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=fce7db78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openup.hk/index.htm?lang=zh-Hant</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"幫唔到我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"試咗先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e9ef2b546d897e6299db1a2de5003a1f4994e7","tid":2303091,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3cf12700011f97b4f87986406eac670808ea4e","tid":2303091,"uid":329350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"諗過唔同嘅死法<br />\n最後都係決定吊頸<br />\n屋企有個位啱啱好<br />\n我講真 睇下我邊日頂唔順就可以去死<br />\n定係點先可以有勇氣勒死條八婆 <br />\n佢死唔去就只好我去死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"警犬仆街，看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=b702f652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=fb51b3e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>  ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}